title: Ep. - 382 - F BOY ISLAND WITH RAE SANNI THE BACHELORETTE WITH ANOTHER BACHELOR PODCAST
description:
Comedian and writer Rae Sanni discusses Bravo’s Real Housewives of Potomac and HBO Max’s F Boy Island, which sets up three single ladies to go through 24 men and distinguish the self-identified f-boys from nice guys.

 

Nick, Dylan, and Pat from Another Bachelor Podcast discuss this season of The Bachelorette.

 

 

Reality Life with Kate Casey
